WEBVTT

00:02:19.319 --> 00:02:21.039
My dear third child

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:22.919
Why did you run off without taking the money?

00:02:23.080 --> 00:02:25.759
Let's give each other another chance.

00:02:25.759 --> 00:02:29.120
Otherwise, I'm afraid we'll both regret it.

00:02:31.520 --> 00:02:33.000
This is never-ending.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:34.400
So annoying.

00:02:34.639 --> 00:02:37.039
I don't need your peanuts.

00:02:48.159 --> 00:02:49.960
Evans, do me a favor.

00:02:50.840 --> 00:02:52.479
I have an account at Citibank.

00:02:52.479 --> 00:02:55.840
Transfer four point two million dollars for me.

00:02:55.840 --> 00:02:57.199
Into my domestic account.

00:02:57.879 --> 00:02:58.840
Please hurry.

00:02:58.840 --> 00:02:59.639
I need it urgently.

00:03:03.800 --> 00:03:04.599
Gotta go.

00:03:05.520 --> 00:03:06.199
Qiu'er

00:03:08.199 --> 00:03:09.599
How's the moving situation going?

00:03:10.400 --> 00:03:12.199
You think finding a house is that easy?

00:03:12.759 --> 00:03:13.680
No need to look.

00:03:14.840 --> 00:03:15.560
Here's an idea.

00:03:15.960 --> 00:03:17.240
I'll buy you a house.

00:03:17.240 --> 00:03:18.560
You can just move in.

00:03:22.280 --> 00:03:24.080
You think I'm a fool, right?

00:03:24.080 --> 00:03:25.599
Are you recording me with your phone?

00:03:25.599 --> 00:03:26.680
My phone is in my hand.

00:03:28.080 --> 00:03:29.240
You hid a camera.

00:03:30.759 --> 00:03:32.479
You want to record me and post it online, huh?

00:03:32.479 --> 00:03:33.479
That's so mean.

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:34.919
I'm not lying to you.

00:03:36.800 --> 00:03:38.439
I know you're not lying.

00:03:38.439 --> 00:03:40.680
To get my aunt back, you'll buy me an apartment.

00:03:40.759 --> 00:03:41.719
I thank you.

00:03:41.719 --> 00:03:42.800
I thank you very much.

00:03:42.800 --> 00:03:44.159
But I'll have to decline.

00:03:44.599 --> 00:03:46.319
Where on earth did you hide the camera?

00:03:48.240 --> 00:03:49.719
I've realized why you never got promoted.

00:03:49.719 --> 00:03:50.759
There's a reason.

00:03:51.879 --> 00:03:53.240
Alright, I'm going back to grab a bite.

00:03:53.240 --> 00:03:54.719
Come over if you're hungry. Don't be shy.

00:03:55.199 --> 00:03:57.759
Mom, can you find me a jacket? It's a bit chilly.

00:03:57.759 --> 00:03:58.919
I'm not joking with you.

00:03:58.919 --> 00:03:59.639
I believe you.

00:03:59.639 --> 00:04:01.080
I believe you very much.

00:04:11.479 --> 00:04:13.199
Wang Fei, come here.

00:04:19.600 --> 00:04:20.839
Wait, what are you doing here?

00:04:20.839 --> 00:04:22.360
Can't I come?

00:04:23.120 --> 00:04:24.079
Come with me.

00:04:24.079 --> 00:04:25.560
Taking you to a great place.

00:04:36.439 --> 00:04:38.879
This is a connection Grandpa Tong pulled for us.

00:04:38.879 --> 00:04:40.720
You know, a film crew.

00:04:41.199 --> 00:04:43.439
So many people want in but can't, you know?

00:04:43.439 --> 00:04:44.480
Hello, hello, hello.

00:04:44.480 --> 00:04:44.879
You must be the director.

00:04:44.879 --> 00:04:45.279
Yes, yes, yes.

00:04:45.279 --> 00:04:46.439
Um, I'm, uh...

00:04:46.439 --> 00:04:48.079
A friend of Teacher Tong.

00:04:48.079 --> 00:04:49.240
This is our son.

00:04:49.240 --> 00:04:50.879
Don't touch other people's things.

00:04:51.040 --> 00:04:52.560
He just wants to see the makeup room.

00:04:52.560 --> 00:04:53.439
No problem, no problem.

00:04:53.439 --> 00:04:54.199
The makeup room is here.

00:04:54.199 --> 00:04:54.600
Great.

00:04:54.600 --> 00:04:55.480
Here, take this.

00:04:55.480 --> 00:04:55.959
Take this.

00:04:55.959 --> 00:04:56.480
You're too kind, too kind.

00:04:56.480 --> 00:04:58.000
This is roast duck, for, for lunch.

00:04:58.000 --> 00:04:58.879
You're busy, you're busy.

00:04:58.879 --> 00:04:59.439
Thank you, thank you.

00:04:59.439 --> 00:05:00.600
Okay, no worries.

00:05:01.800 --> 00:05:02.759
Touching people's stuff.

00:05:02.759 --> 00:05:04.800
You'll end up breaking something.

00:05:05.240 --> 00:05:07.680
This makeup room is just a big bus.

00:05:09.040 --> 00:05:10.720
Keep quiet. Don't talk once you're up there.

00:05:10.720 --> 00:05:11.319
Okay.

00:05:12.120 --> 00:05:13.279
Teacher, after you.

00:05:15.879 --> 00:05:17.160
This armor is plastic too.

00:05:17.160 --> 00:05:19.000
Why do you care if it's plastic?

00:05:19.000 --> 00:05:20.040
How do you fight in it?

00:05:20.279 --> 00:05:20.959
Wait, Dad.

00:05:21.040 --> 00:05:23.360
Why did you bring me to see a makeup room?

00:05:24.040 --> 00:05:25.639
Aren't you interested in, you know, face painting...

00:05:25.639 --> 00:05:27.759
...and makeup and all that stuff?

00:05:27.759 --> 00:05:29.079
So I brought you to see.

00:05:29.079 --> 00:05:31.639
How professional makeup artists work.

00:05:32.160 --> 00:05:33.120
Let me tell you.

00:05:33.399 --> 00:05:35.759
These people aren't just high schoolers.

00:05:35.959 --> 00:05:38.279
They all went to proper universities.

00:05:38.279 --> 00:05:40.519
They have professional training, you know?

00:05:40.920 --> 00:05:42.439
Anyway, if you're interested in this,

00:05:42.439 --> 00:05:46.120
Your mom and I will overcome all obstacles

00:05:46.120 --> 00:05:47.480
to create the conditions for you.

00:05:47.800 --> 00:05:49.120
But you have to take the college entrance exam.

00:05:49.120 --> 00:05:50.879
You have to go to university, understand?

00:05:52.079 --> 00:05:53.079
This kid.

00:06:02.720 --> 00:06:03.800
What are you doing here?

00:06:04.480 --> 00:06:06.839
Uh, we're friends of Director Liu.

00:06:06.839 --> 00:06:07.720
Just here to look around.

00:06:08.120 --> 00:06:08.560
Okay.

00:06:08.560 --> 00:06:09.439
To learn.

00:06:13.920 --> 00:06:16.480
Is this real or fake?

00:06:16.600 --> 00:06:17.480
Just glued on.

00:06:35.079 --> 00:06:35.920
It's done.

00:06:44.959 --> 00:06:45.600
Eat up.

00:06:49.000 --> 00:06:50.279
Eat, take it.

00:06:52.360 --> 00:06:53.600
Look, we went to see it today.

00:06:53.600 --> 00:06:55.639
Those professional makeup artists, right?

00:06:55.839 --> 00:06:57.720
Look at their work.

00:06:57.920 --> 00:06:59.680
They use that makeup.

00:06:59.920 --> 00:07:01.519
You'd have to learn some chemistry.

00:07:01.759 --> 00:07:02.480
Right?

00:07:02.680 --> 00:07:03.639
Look at how they...

00:07:03.639 --> 00:07:06.399
...apply lines, draw eyebrows, it all takes precision.

00:07:06.399 --> 00:07:08.120
You'd have to learn some art, right?

00:07:08.120 --> 00:07:09.519
And say it's a modern drama.

00:07:09.519 --> 00:07:10.959
If it were a period drama,

00:07:10.959 --> 00:07:12.560
you'd have to learn some history.

00:07:12.560 --> 00:07:13.920
And some geography, right?

00:07:13.920 --> 00:07:17.079
Yeah, after seeing it, I'm not interested.

00:07:17.360 --> 00:07:18.720
I also think that stuff...

00:07:18.720 --> 00:07:20.279
...isn't that great.

00:07:20.480 --> 00:07:21.199
Alright then.

00:07:21.959 --> 00:07:22.839
Later on,

00:07:23.360 --> 00:07:25.399
have your Uncle Qiu'er contact their school.

00:07:25.639 --> 00:07:27.560
I'll take you to see the Finance College.

00:07:27.560 --> 00:07:29.600
We'll check out their library,

00:07:29.720 --> 00:07:31.560
dorms, cafeteria,

00:07:31.560 --> 00:07:32.439
see what the campus is like,

00:07:32.439 --> 00:07:33.319
how people date and stuff.

00:07:33.319 --> 00:07:34.000
Stop with the hassle.

00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:35.240
I go to watch people date?

00:07:35.399 --> 00:07:36.319
Right? No.

00:07:36.319 --> 00:07:37.639
If you still don't like it,

00:07:37.639 --> 00:07:40.319
then we'll go where your second uncle works.

00:07:40.319 --> 00:07:41.399
We'll go to the Central Business District.

00:07:41.399 --> 00:07:42.879
See their high-end,

00:07:42.879 --> 00:07:44.160
what their offices are like.

00:07:44.319 --> 00:07:45.560
Stop with the hassle.

00:07:46.399 --> 00:07:47.480
Wait, Dad, are you willing to listen

00:07:47.480 --> 00:07:48.720
to my real thoughts?

00:07:49.120 --> 00:07:51.199
Speak, speak, speak.

00:07:54.240 --> 00:07:55.720
I've thought about it myself.

00:07:58.079 --> 00:08:00.839
It's not that I'm saying

00:08:00.839 --> 00:08:02.319
I absolutely must

00:08:02.519 --> 00:08:04.079
not go to university.

00:08:04.240 --> 00:08:05.879
Great, then let's just take the exam.

00:08:05.879 --> 00:08:07.360
No, no, yes, yes, let me finish first.

00:08:07.360 --> 00:08:09.079
Speak, speak, I'm willing to listen.

00:08:09.079 --> 00:08:09.639
Go on.

00:08:11.240 --> 00:08:12.480
Now everyone says

00:08:12.480 --> 00:08:14.120
that kids must go to college.

00:08:14.120 --> 00:08:15.680
Then what is the meaning of taking the college entrance exam?

00:08:18.680 --> 00:08:20.399
Just like there are many things I can't figure out.

00:08:20.480 --> 00:08:22.000
I can make money doing live streaming now.

00:08:22.000 --> 00:08:23.920
But if it's just for the sake of making money,

00:08:23.920 --> 00:08:25.600
then what is the meaning of my live streaming?

00:08:25.600 --> 00:08:26.600
So in the end,

00:08:26.600 --> 00:08:28.399
what is the meaning of making money?

00:08:29.199 --> 00:08:30.600
I am only nineteen years old now.

00:08:30.600 --> 00:08:33.039
I still have decades left to live.

00:08:33.159 --> 00:08:35.200
Then for every single day that I live,

00:08:35.840 --> 00:08:36.960
what is the meaning of it?

00:08:38.480 --> 00:08:39.360
No, you... you...

00:08:39.360 --> 00:08:40.759
You are concerned about my future.

00:08:40.759 --> 00:08:41.320
Yes.

00:08:41.320 --> 00:08:42.279
What about Uncle Qiu'er?

00:08:42.279 --> 00:08:43.559
He's concerned about the house, right?

00:08:43.559 --> 00:08:45.519
Second Uncle is just concerned about his career.

00:08:45.919 --> 00:08:48.320
Teacher Mao is all about enrollment rates every day.

00:08:48.320 --> 00:08:50.240
And the classmates are concerned about their scores.

00:08:50.960 --> 00:08:52.559
It seems like everyone is just focused on this one thing,

00:08:52.559 --> 00:08:53.720
running forward with their heads down.

00:08:53.720 --> 00:08:55.840
Is this one thing the entirety of life?

00:08:55.840 --> 00:08:56.960
Obviously not.

00:08:56.960 --> 00:08:58.320
But what I see right now is,

00:08:58.320 --> 00:09:01.080
everyone is living their lives just like ants.

00:09:01.440 --> 00:09:02.799
So what is the meaning of life?

00:09:02.799 --> 00:09:04.200
What are we pursuing?

00:09:06.639 --> 00:09:08.360
I don't understand. I really don't.

00:09:14.120 --> 00:09:15.559
This question is worth thinking about.

00:09:18.440 --> 00:09:20.039
You, don't give me any of that talk about

00:09:20.039 --> 00:09:21.799
what's meaningful and what's not.

00:09:22.120 --> 00:09:24.480
Since talking nicely to you doesn't work,

00:09:24.960 --> 00:09:26.320
then from now on,

00:09:26.320 --> 00:09:27.679
you will listen to me.

00:09:28.600 --> 00:09:29.960
All this messy stuff,

00:09:31.159 --> 00:09:32.559
I'm confiscating it for now.

00:09:33.000 --> 00:09:34.960
When you get into college later,

00:09:35.240 --> 00:09:36.480
I'll give it back to you.

00:09:38.559 --> 00:09:40.399
I've made you too comfortable in the past.

00:09:40.639 --> 00:09:41.799
Take these headphones off.

00:09:42.440 --> 00:09:43.480
Hand them over.

00:09:50.559 --> 00:09:52.759
Don't give me this silent protest.

00:09:52.759 --> 00:09:54.360
So many revolutionary martyrs,

00:09:54.360 --> 00:09:57.000
in extremely arduous environments,

00:09:57.000 --> 00:09:58.399
created great causes.

00:09:58.519 --> 00:09:59.879
You are far from that.

00:09:59.879 --> 00:10:01.919
Didn't you say to strike a balance between work and rest?

00:10:01.919 --> 00:10:03.200
Don't join in the fuss.

00:10:03.399 --> 00:10:04.919
Get ready to perm my hair.

00:10:05.039 --> 00:10:06.639
I'm getting it ready for you.

00:10:24.039 --> 00:10:26.120
The tone you use with our son from now on,

00:10:26.120 --> 00:10:27.360
can't it be a bit gentler?

00:10:27.360 --> 00:10:29.080
Is he your biological son or not?

00:10:29.279 --> 00:10:30.720
I'm telling you, being soft doesn't work.

00:10:30.720 --> 00:10:31.840
We have to be tough.

00:10:32.000 --> 00:10:33.120
I just can't stand his...

00:10:33.120 --> 00:10:35.039
look at him, just drifting along day after day.

00:10:37.200 --> 00:10:39.559
When I was learning to roast ducks back in the day,

00:10:40.039 --> 00:10:41.440
how much hardship did I endure?

00:10:41.440 --> 00:10:43.600
How many beatings did I take? Right?

00:10:44.039 --> 00:10:46.039
They are happy enough now.

00:10:46.039 --> 00:10:47.679
Stop always talking about "back in the day."

00:10:47.679 --> 00:10:49.600
That was ages ago.

00:10:49.600 --> 00:10:51.600
Your son is going through a rebellious phase now.

00:10:51.600 --> 00:10:53.039
Don't make things worse.

00:10:53.039 --> 00:10:54.559
Rebel? Let's see if he dares to rebel.

00:10:55.240 --> 00:10:56.480
Where can he rebel to?

00:10:57.320 --> 00:10:59.399
After all, he is our biological son, right?

00:10:59.600 --> 00:11:00.600
What are you afraid of?

00:11:01.840 --> 00:11:03.000
I just don't believe it.

00:11:03.879 --> 00:11:05.240
I've accompanied him growing up all this time.

00:11:05.600 --> 00:11:08.399
I'll grit my teeth and accompany him for another two years.

00:11:08.399 --> 00:11:10.759
I don't believe I can't get him into college.

00:11:10.759 --> 00:11:11.679
Accompany, accompany, accompany.

00:11:12.200 --> 00:11:13.240
Just wait a moment.

00:11:14.600 --> 00:11:16.440
You... go in and see what he's doing.

00:11:17.159 --> 00:11:18.320
Fix this up.

00:11:33.639 --> 00:11:34.240
Your coffee.

00:11:34.240 --> 00:11:34.799
Thank you.

00:11:40.720 --> 00:11:43.200
A coffee shop with so many books.

00:11:43.399 --> 00:11:44.799
It's a place for studying.

00:11:44.960 --> 00:11:46.919
Hello sir, what would you like?

00:11:48.879 --> 00:11:52.360
I heard there's a tutoring class here, right?

00:11:53.200 --> 00:11:54.399
No, there isn't.

00:11:57.600 --> 00:11:59.360
No? But this is the address.

00:12:00.360 --> 00:12:04.759
However, there is an interest class.

00:12:05.879 --> 00:12:07.120
What kind of interest class?

00:12:07.440 --> 00:12:08.480
It's just that our boss,

00:12:08.480 --> 00:12:10.600
learned some coffee techniques abroad,

00:12:10.600 --> 00:12:14.080
and often shares them with interested people.

00:12:16.840 --> 00:12:20.440
I can see that you, Mr. Wang, love drinking coffee.

00:12:20.639 --> 00:12:21.440
Right?

00:12:26.720 --> 00:12:27.960
You love it, don't you?

00:12:31.159 --> 00:12:31.799
Yes.

00:12:31.799 --> 00:12:33.679
I... I... I do love drinking coffee.

00:12:33.799 --> 00:12:35.960
I... if I don't drink coffee,

00:12:35.960 --> 00:12:36.919
I can't even sleep.

00:12:36.919 --> 00:12:37.759
That's great.

00:12:37.759 --> 00:12:38.879
Then you can sign up for

00:12:38.879 --> 00:12:40.960
a prepaid membership card for our shop.

00:12:40.960 --> 00:12:43.879
There are options for 8,000, 10,000, and 20,000.

00:12:44.039 --> 00:12:45.120
After getting the card,

00:12:45.120 --> 00:12:46.720
when you buy coffee at our shop,

00:12:46.720 --> 00:12:48.279
you will get a corresponding discount.

00:12:50.039 --> 00:12:52.200
Well, no...

00:12:52.200 --> 00:12:55.360
Besides teaching about coffee here,

00:12:55.480 --> 00:12:57.759
don't you also teach something else?

00:13:01.080 --> 00:13:02.080
Mr. Wang,

00:13:02.080 --> 00:13:03.159
here with us,

00:13:03.159 --> 00:13:05.639
you can learn the best coffee techniques.

00:13:11.159 --> 00:13:12.679
Alright, take a look at the form.

00:13:12.679 --> 00:13:13.799
What would you like to study?

00:13:13.799 --> 00:13:15.120
Just check the boxes.

00:13:18.240 --> 00:13:19.360
Right here, see?

00:13:20.200 --> 00:13:22.759
This sour mocha is Chinese, right?

00:13:22.759 --> 00:13:23.720
We have to check this one.

00:13:24.240 --> 00:13:27.080
Mexican coffee is math.

00:13:27.399 --> 00:13:30.159
Colombian coffee is foreign language.

00:13:30.159 --> 00:13:33.039
Arabica coffee, this is politics.

00:13:33.559 --> 00:13:36.039
We'll skip art, music, and dance.

00:13:36.480 --> 00:13:38.879
Then... then just these subjects.

00:13:39.799 --> 00:13:40.960
Mr. Wang.

00:13:41.679 --> 00:13:43.720
Our interest class teachers

00:13:43.720 --> 00:13:45.840
are all top-tier in the industry.

00:13:45.840 --> 00:13:49.159
The teachers for small and large classes are also different.

00:13:49.320 --> 00:13:51.159
You know what I mean?

00:13:52.240 --> 00:13:53.080
I understand.

00:13:54.480 --> 00:13:55.600
I get it.

00:13:56.440 --> 00:13:57.799
For my son.

00:13:58.360 --> 00:13:59.240
I'll transfer it to you.

00:13:59.240 --> 00:13:59.799
Okay.

00:14:00.279 --> 00:14:00.960
Did it go through?

00:14:00.960 --> 00:14:01.759
It's here.

00:14:02.519 --> 00:14:04.960
Um, can we get an invoice?

00:14:05.960 --> 00:14:06.480
An invoice?

00:14:06.480 --> 00:14:07.360
Who's in charge here?

00:14:10.559 --> 00:14:13.240
Hello, can I help you?

00:14:13.240 --> 00:14:14.720
We've received reports from the public

00:14:14.720 --> 00:14:16.039
that you're using this cafe

00:14:16.039 --> 00:14:18.120
to conduct paid tutoring under the guise of membership.

00:14:18.120 --> 00:14:19.240
We'd like to verify this.

00:14:19.240 --> 00:14:20.519
Please come with us now.

00:14:22.120 --> 00:14:23.120
Wait, miss.

00:14:23.120 --> 00:14:25.120
I just paid the money!

00:14:27.960 --> 00:14:29.720
If he had said anything else,

00:14:29.720 --> 00:14:30.519
I might have believed him.

00:14:30.519 --> 00:14:31.799
But leading with buying a house?

00:14:31.799 --> 00:14:34.519
Is that something a normal person would do?

00:14:34.519 --> 00:14:35.320
Tell me.

00:14:35.600 --> 00:14:37.879
How can he not be ashamed?

00:14:38.240 --> 00:14:39.399
Qiu'er, here's what you do.

00:14:40.120 --> 00:14:41.679
If he says he'll buy you a house,

00:14:41.679 --> 00:14:43.279
you actually take him to look.

00:14:43.360 --> 00:14:44.159
See how he

00:14:44.159 --> 00:14:45.679
talks his way out of it then.

00:14:45.679 --> 00:14:47.120
Right, hear what he says.

00:14:47.120 --> 00:14:48.279
Play along with his scheme.

00:14:48.279 --> 00:14:49.759
I don't have time for this. I want to sleep.

00:14:49.759 --> 00:14:50.840
Coming!

00:14:51.600 --> 00:14:52.480
Weiguo.

00:14:52.480 --> 00:14:53.480
Well, look at that.

00:14:53.480 --> 00:14:54.360
Morning, Brother Dayang.

00:14:54.600 --> 00:14:56.279
See, there's a connection now, see?

00:14:57.360 --> 00:14:58.360
Are you ready?

00:14:59.360 --> 00:15:00.960
Ready for what? What's up?

00:15:00.960 --> 00:15:01.799
To go see a house.

00:15:05.279 --> 00:15:06.279
Weiguo.

00:15:06.440 --> 00:15:08.799
If you keep joking about the same thing,

00:15:08.799 --> 00:15:09.519
it stops being funny.

00:15:09.519 --> 00:15:10.960
Who's joking about something this boring?

00:15:10.960 --> 00:15:12.159
The real estate agent is here.

00:15:12.279 --> 00:15:13.000
Xiao Hu.

00:15:16.279 --> 00:15:18.159
Hu Wan, from Chenghe Real Estate.

00:15:18.159 --> 00:15:18.919
Hello.

00:15:19.240 --> 00:15:20.399
Hu, as in the character for 'moon'.

00:15:20.399 --> 00:15:21.039
They don't need one.

00:15:21.039 --> 00:15:21.679
Just for reference, we're all friends.

00:15:21.679 --> 00:15:22.159
Here you go, brother.

00:15:22.159 --> 00:15:23.279
No, no, no need.

00:15:23.279 --> 00:15:24.679
We'll wait outside. Hurry up.

00:15:25.279 --> 00:15:26.080
Weiguo.

00:15:26.679 --> 00:15:29.799
You see, my lottery shop is a bit cramped.

00:15:29.799 --> 00:15:31.039
Given our friendship,

00:15:31.039 --> 00:15:32.480
you should find me a bigger place.

00:15:34.360 --> 00:15:35.919
No... Huh, what does this mean?

00:15:42.360 --> 00:15:44.840
This is... he's serious.

00:15:45.200 --> 00:15:47.440
You should take him seriously too. Go on.

00:15:47.440 --> 00:15:48.360
Go, go, go.

00:15:48.759 --> 00:15:49.600
Alright then.

00:15:49.600 --> 00:15:51.000
I'll go scout ahead.

00:15:51.000 --> 00:15:51.799
I'm off, brother.

00:15:51.799 --> 00:15:52.440
Take it easy.

00:15:52.440 --> 00:15:52.879
Bye, Brother Dayang.

00:15:52.879 --> 00:15:53.519
Bye, bye.

00:15:54.600 --> 00:15:56.320
What's going on here?

00:15:56.879 --> 00:15:58.799
He's not terminally ill,

00:15:58.799 --> 00:16:01.039
and suddenly feeling charitable before he dies, is he?

00:16:01.679 --> 00:16:03.000
If he really is terminally ill,

00:16:03.000 --> 00:16:04.399
he should go find a place to die.

00:16:04.919 --> 00:16:06.320
Don't cause trouble for me here.

00:16:06.320 --> 00:16:08.399
What's wrong? Family trouble again?

00:16:11.360 --> 00:16:13.399
If I tell you, you'll just go blabbering everywhere.

00:16:13.759 --> 00:16:15.879
I'm just concerned about you, buddy.

00:16:18.919 --> 00:16:20.360
You're really buying me a house?

00:16:20.480 --> 00:16:22.279
I thought you were joking.

00:16:23.600 --> 00:16:25.039
Do you know Beijing housing prices?

00:16:25.039 --> 00:16:26.000
They're not cheap.

00:16:26.440 --> 00:16:27.720
Maybe buy somewhere farther out.

00:16:27.720 --> 00:16:29.120
But it can't be too far from the hospital.

00:16:29.120 --> 00:16:30.480
You know about my dad's illness.

00:16:30.960 --> 00:16:32.440
The house isn't a free gift.

00:16:32.440 --> 00:16:33.519
There are conditions.

00:16:33.639 --> 00:16:36.039
I want you to take care of Auntie in her old age.

00:16:36.200 --> 00:16:37.320
That's no problem.

00:16:37.320 --> 00:16:38.039
Besides,

00:16:38.039 --> 00:16:39.360
there's also Xiaofangzi and her husband.

00:16:39.360 --> 00:16:40.279
Let me tell you something.

00:16:41.279 --> 00:16:43.639
I don't trust that Tang Zhixin.

00:16:44.399 --> 00:16:45.919
You're being too judgmental.

00:16:46.039 --> 00:16:48.240
No matter what, she's her own daughter, he's her own son-in-law.

00:16:48.240 --> 00:16:49.159
They wouldn't just abandon their own mother.

00:16:49.159 --> 00:16:51.039
Taking care of Auntie is our duty.

00:16:51.039 --> 00:16:52.240
If I took your house for that,

00:16:52.240 --> 00:16:53.360
people would laugh at me.

00:16:55.000 --> 00:16:56.639
Don't talk to me about duty.

00:16:56.639 --> 00:16:58.080
I only believe in equivalent exchange.

00:16:58.440 --> 00:16:59.799
When the house is handed over,

00:16:59.799 --> 00:17:01.120
I'll sign a contract with you.

00:17:01.120 --> 00:17:03.440
If Auntie suffers any mistreatment,

00:17:03.519 --> 00:17:04.839
I'll take the house back immediately.

00:17:05.559 --> 00:17:08.160
Second, do you know why I'm giving it to you

00:17:08.160 --> 00:17:09.200
and not someone else?

00:17:10.799 --> 00:17:11.880
Because you...

00:17:11.880 --> 00:17:13.799
are the most cowardly and greedy.

00:17:13.960 --> 00:17:16.119
A coward, even with bad intentions,

00:17:16.119 --> 00:17:17.119
can't commit any great evil.

00:17:17.119 --> 00:17:18.799
A greedy person cares about gains and losses.

00:17:18.799 --> 00:17:20.079
So entrusting the house to you

00:17:20.079 --> 00:17:21.200
makes me feel most at ease.

00:17:22.440 --> 00:17:23.440
Third, I'm telling you,

00:17:23.599 --> 00:17:25.160
you must be careful of that Tang Zhixin.

00:17:25.680 --> 00:17:27.200
When Auntie was bedridden,

00:17:27.200 --> 00:17:28.319
the second time he met me,

00:17:28.319 --> 00:17:29.480
he wanted to talk business.

00:17:29.839 --> 00:17:31.759
It shows he values profit.

00:17:31.759 --> 00:17:32.960
And he doesn't know how to hide it.

00:17:33.480 --> 00:17:34.920
So in the future, any benefits

00:17:34.920 --> 00:17:35.960
must absolutely not go to him.

00:17:36.119 --> 00:17:38.400
Even if Auntie begs you. Understand?

00:17:39.680 --> 00:17:40.279
Let's go.

00:17:41.960 --> 00:17:44.440
Wait, were you complimenting or insulting me just now?

00:17:51.039 --> 00:17:51.759
Can I ask you something?

00:17:51.759 --> 00:17:52.920
How much are you actually planning to pay?

00:17:52.920 --> 00:17:54.160
I'm really nervous about this.

00:17:54.400 --> 00:17:55.119
Qiu'er.

00:17:55.200 --> 00:17:56.680
I want to confirm something with you.

00:17:56.880 --> 00:17:58.359
After I buy you the house,

00:17:58.359 --> 00:17:59.920
will your urgent problems be solved?

00:17:59.920 --> 00:18:01.000
Not exactly.

00:18:01.160 --> 00:18:02.440
I want a promotion and a raise.

00:18:02.519 --> 00:18:03.640
My dad needs medical treatment.

00:18:03.640 --> 00:18:04.839
My mom wants to buy a nice burial plot.

00:18:04.839 --> 00:18:06.000
My wife wants to have a baby.

00:18:06.319 --> 00:18:07.640
That's a lot of problems.

00:18:07.640 --> 00:18:08.680
There's more.

00:18:08.680 --> 00:18:11.000
But the top priority, ultimately, is the house.

00:18:11.200 --> 00:18:11.960
Alright then.

00:18:12.400 --> 00:18:14.079
After we solve your problem first,

00:18:14.079 --> 00:18:16.039
then we'll talk about Wang Chunsheng and Li Lianbao.

00:18:16.160 --> 00:18:17.480
Help me pass a message to them.

00:18:17.480 --> 00:18:18.759
Tell them if they have any conditions,

00:18:18.759 --> 00:18:19.759
they can bring them to me.

00:18:20.759 --> 00:18:21.720
I understand, Weiguo.

00:18:21.720 --> 00:18:22.680
You're just being shy.

00:18:22.799 --> 00:18:24.720
You didn't just come back for Auntie.

00:18:24.720 --> 00:18:25.599
You came back for us too.

00:18:25.799 --> 00:18:27.559
You genuinely want to reconcile with us.

00:18:27.559 --> 00:18:28.079
Right?

00:18:28.240 --> 00:18:30.799
Don't get me wrong, I don't want to make up with you.

00:18:31.359 --> 00:18:34.000
I just want to stay with Auntie a bit longer.

00:18:34.400 --> 00:18:36.559
As for Wang Chunsheng and Li Lianbao,

00:18:36.799 --> 00:18:38.799
I just want to confirm if they're trustworthy.

00:18:38.799 --> 00:18:40.480
What do you mean, trustworthy?

00:18:40.720 --> 00:18:42.400
We grew up together, we're brothers.

00:18:42.400 --> 00:18:44.000
How could we not be trustworthy?

00:18:44.319 --> 00:18:46.240
Just think about that fight Big Brother got into as a kid...

00:18:46.240 --> 00:18:47.200
Alright, enough joking around.

00:18:48.039 --> 00:18:48.839
Weiguo.

00:18:52.519 --> 00:18:54.440
If you don't want to hear about the past,

00:18:54.440 --> 00:18:55.559
I won't bring it up.

00:18:56.640 --> 00:18:57.920
I just hope us brothers

00:18:57.920 --> 00:18:59.240
can sit down and have a proper talk.

00:18:59.640 --> 00:19:01.519
Let bygones be bygones.

00:19:02.160 --> 00:19:02.880
Okay?

00:19:05.160 --> 00:19:06.200
Take Big Brother now, for instance.

00:19:06.200 --> 00:19:06.960
Actually, actually...

00:19:06.960 --> 00:19:08.640
He's mainly worried about his kid.

00:19:08.640 --> 00:19:09.759
For his son, Feifei,

00:19:09.759 --> 00:19:10.960
he'd spare no expense.

00:19:13.400 --> 00:19:14.119
Feifei.

00:19:14.240 --> 00:19:15.720
Yeah, his son.

00:19:15.960 --> 00:19:16.680
I know.

00:19:18.960 --> 00:19:19.880
Feifei.

00:19:22.880 --> 00:19:23.759
Weiguo.

00:19:23.880 --> 00:19:24.640
Weiguo.

00:19:27.799 --> 00:19:29.720
Don't be fooled by how Big Brother always scowls

00:19:29.720 --> 00:19:31.039
and glares at Feifei.

00:19:31.599 --> 00:19:32.079
Anyone home?

00:19:32.079 --> 00:19:34.279
Actually, Feifei is the apple of his eye.

00:19:34.279 --> 00:19:36.319
Feifei had a serious illness as a child.

00:19:36.319 --> 00:19:36.839
Anyone home?

00:19:36.839 --> 00:19:38.480
He was out of school for a whole year.

00:19:38.640 --> 00:19:40.640
So he's a bit older than kids his age.

00:19:40.640 --> 00:19:42.000
And because of that,

00:19:42.000 --> 00:19:43.759
Big Brother feels even more pressure.

00:19:44.920 --> 00:19:46.960
What's the big deal?

00:19:57.559 --> 00:19:59.200
Sorry about that.

00:20:58.119 --> 00:21:00.319
That's basically how it is with Big Brother.

00:21:00.920 --> 00:21:02.319
What about Lianbao?

00:21:03.519 --> 00:21:05.640
His wife ran off with a foreigner.

00:21:05.880 --> 00:21:07.240
The kid went with the mom.

00:21:07.559 --> 00:21:10.079
I heard that foreigner runs a big international fund.

00:21:10.079 --> 00:21:11.240
He's loaded.

00:21:11.799 --> 00:21:12.759
Other than that,

00:21:12.759 --> 00:21:14.359
he doesn't seem to have any worries.

00:21:16.920 --> 00:21:19.680
Old Chen, we're old friends.

00:21:19.680 --> 00:21:20.880
What do you mean by this?

00:21:20.960 --> 00:21:22.839
Just say what's on your mind.

00:21:28.279 --> 00:21:29.880
Yuanyuan, I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

00:21:29.880 --> 00:21:31.640
Daddy's work is just too busy.

00:21:31.640 --> 00:21:32.920
Look, so many people are fighting

00:21:32.920 --> 00:21:34.400
to work with Daddy.

00:21:35.079 --> 00:21:36.119
Just wait a few more years for me.

00:21:36.119 --> 00:21:37.240
Wait until Daddy's work,

00:21:37.240 --> 00:21:39.160
this career, gets bigger and bigger.

00:21:39.160 --> 00:21:40.680
I'll leave it all to you, okay?

00:21:41.119 --> 00:21:42.480
Daddy's the best!

00:21:43.400 --> 00:21:44.400
As for Second Brother,

00:21:44.400 --> 00:21:45.079
Where else do you want to go play?

00:21:45.079 --> 00:21:45.839
he's still the same.

00:21:46.119 --> 00:21:47.680
Sharp tongue, soft heart.

00:21:48.039 --> 00:21:49.880
But if he actually gets gentle,

00:21:49.880 --> 00:21:51.440
it's actually a bit scary.

00:21:52.599 --> 00:21:53.759
Just between you and me,

00:21:54.319 --> 00:21:55.359
that feeling

00:21:55.359 --> 00:21:56.400
is a bit like

00:21:57.119 --> 00:21:58.920
an African baboon trying to meow.

00:21:59.119 --> 00:22:00.839
You just don't know what's gotten into him.

00:22:01.000 --> 00:22:02.240
Everything feels off.

00:22:09.240 --> 00:22:09.799
Tom.

00:22:12.160 --> 00:22:13.319
Yuanyuan, come down now.

00:22:14.759 --> 00:22:15.519
Jenny.

00:22:18.200 --> 00:22:19.759
You gave her something cold to eat, didn't you?

00:22:19.759 --> 00:22:20.599
Why don't you just install

00:22:20.599 --> 00:22:21.680
a camera on her?

00:22:23.119 --> 00:22:25.559
Yuanyuan, how could you forget this?

00:22:26.960 --> 00:22:28.000
Bye, Daddy.

00:22:28.079 --> 00:22:28.720
Bye.

00:22:29.440 --> 00:22:30.839
We're going home now.

00:22:30.839 --> 00:22:31.200
Let's go.

00:22:31.200 --> 00:22:31.640
Go.

00:22:35.319 --> 00:22:36.319
Did you drink any water?

00:22:36.319 --> 00:22:37.759
Your water bottle is still full.

00:22:37.839 --> 00:22:38.759
I just filled it.

00:22:39.119 --> 00:22:40.119
Really?

00:22:40.680 --> 00:22:41.440
Are you tired?

00:22:41.440 --> 00:22:43.200
I made you some Portuguese egg tarts.

00:22:43.200 --> 00:22:44.079
I made them myself.

00:22:44.079 --> 00:22:44.720
Really.

00:22:44.720 --> 00:22:45.720
Yes, yes, yes.

00:22:46.640 --> 00:22:47.759
Hurry up and go inside.

00:23:20.039 --> 00:23:21.119
Here, this way.

00:23:23.200 --> 00:23:24.519
It looks nice from the outside.

00:23:24.519 --> 00:23:25.799
Why is it still like this inside?

00:23:25.880 --> 00:23:26.559
Bro.

00:23:26.559 --> 00:23:28.079
It's much better than before now.

00:23:28.079 --> 00:23:30.519
During the coal-to-electricity conversion, it wasn't this clean.

00:23:30.519 --> 00:23:32.839
Look at the road now, how wide it is.

00:23:33.720 --> 00:23:36.200
It's here, Bro, over here.

00:23:40.880 --> 00:23:43.039
Look, right here.

00:23:51.279 --> 00:23:52.359
Bro, look.

00:23:52.359 --> 00:23:53.920
Retro courtyard, private garden.

00:23:53.920 --> 00:23:55.799
In the bustling city, yet away from the noise.

00:23:55.799 --> 00:23:58.440
This house is the king of value for money.

00:23:58.440 --> 00:23:59.839
Just a bit small.

00:24:01.359 --> 00:24:02.200
Weiguo.

00:24:03.119 --> 00:24:03.960
You...

00:24:05.759 --> 00:24:08.079
My house outside the Fifth Ring is big,

00:24:08.240 --> 00:24:09.839
and the area is convenient.

00:24:09.839 --> 00:24:11.519
But I always feel something's off.

00:24:11.799 --> 00:24:13.200
Later, I figured it out.

00:24:13.359 --> 00:24:14.839
If I want some fried liver and baozi,

00:24:14.839 --> 00:24:15.920
I have to come back here to buy it.

00:24:15.920 --> 00:24:17.200
That place doesn't have this flavor.

00:24:17.559 --> 00:24:20.680
So, how about we consider this as one of our options?

00:24:20.680 --> 00:24:21.720
What do you think?

00:24:21.720 --> 00:24:23.119
Okay, it's alright, it's alright.

00:24:23.119 --> 00:24:24.400
Forget it, let's not look anymore.

00:24:26.680 --> 00:24:27.680
We're not looking anymore?

00:24:28.200 --> 00:24:29.799
Can't you see how crude this is?

00:24:30.119 --> 00:24:30.680
Alright then.

00:24:30.680 --> 00:24:31.759
Take us to see

00:24:31.759 --> 00:24:33.079
a house with better conditions.

00:24:33.519 --> 00:24:35.640
Bro, a place with better conditions

00:24:35.640 --> 00:24:37.759
costs more, the value isn't good.

00:24:37.759 --> 00:24:39.759
I never look at value for money when I buy things.

00:24:39.759 --> 00:24:40.279
Money...

00:24:40.279 --> 00:24:42.200
should be spent on things that aren't a good deal.

00:24:42.200 --> 00:24:43.480
That's what makes it money, understand?

00:24:43.799 --> 00:24:45.680
Look at this, it's like a maze.

00:24:46.039 --> 00:24:47.519
You call this value for money?

00:24:48.960 --> 00:24:51.079
Understood, bro. I'll go make a call.

00:25:13.400 --> 00:25:14.720
Get up, get up now.

00:25:14.799 --> 00:25:15.559
Get up.

00:25:16.359 --> 00:25:16.880
Wang Fei.

00:25:17.119 --> 00:25:18.319
Hurry up and get out of bed.

00:25:18.319 --> 00:25:20.400
It's only five o'clock, even the birds aren't up.

00:25:20.400 --> 00:25:22.240
