00:25:22.240 --> 00:25:22.920
Mom!

00:25:22.920 --> 00:25:23.920
Don't call your mom.

00:25:23.920 --> 00:25:25.559
Your mom can't handle this matter.

00:25:25.920 --> 00:25:27.079
Starting today,

00:25:27.200 --> 00:25:28.680
we both get up at five o'clock.

00:25:28.680 --> 00:25:30.359
I'll accompany you, we'll memorize vocabulary.

00:25:30.359 --> 00:25:31.319
Let me tell you,

00:25:31.480 --> 00:25:33.160
the early bird catches the worm.

00:25:33.160 --> 00:25:34.759
While others are resting,

00:25:34.759 --> 00:25:37.319
is the best time for you to catch up, you know?

00:25:37.319 --> 00:25:38.559
Get out of bed and put your shoes on, quick.

00:25:39.039 --> 00:25:40.920
Fine, right away, right away.

00:25:41.759 --> 00:25:44.400
Yeah, the early worm gets eaten by the bird.

00:25:44.839 --> 00:25:45.920
Hurry up.

00:25:47.960 --> 00:25:50.640
Bored, bored.

00:25:52.680 --> 00:25:53.880
B O R E D.

00:25:53.880 --> 00:25:56.119
Bored, bored.

00:25:58.880 --> 00:26:02.240
Bird, right? That means little bird, doesn't it?

00:26:04.160 --> 00:26:05.720
What little bird?

00:26:06.279 --> 00:26:07.319
Bored.

00:26:07.920 --> 00:26:09.200
Don't try to fool me.

00:26:09.759 --> 00:26:12.160
I've learned a fair bit of English here and there.

00:26:12.160 --> 00:26:13.839
Bird, bird.

00:26:13.839 --> 00:26:15.160
B I R D.

00:26:15.359 --> 00:26:18.799
Bored. I'm not lying, look.

00:26:20.160 --> 00:26:21.240
Bored.

00:26:24.200 --> 00:26:24.960
That's me.

00:26:25.880 --> 00:26:26.640
Don't have so much...

00:26:26.640 --> 00:26:29.000
Don't have so much nonsense.

00:26:30.720 --> 00:26:31.839
Bored.

00:26:32.000 --> 00:26:33.200
B O R E D.

00:26:33.200 --> 00:26:35.319
Bored, bored.

00:26:35.559 --> 00:26:39.359
Bored, bored, bored.

00:26:39.720 --> 00:26:40.759
B O R E D.

00:26:40.759 --> 00:26:41.960
Bored.

00:26:42.160 --> 00:26:43.079
Bored.

00:26:43.279 --> 00:26:44.160
Bored.

00:26:44.720 --> 00:26:47.920
Dull, dull, dull.

00:26:48.400 --> 00:26:51.920
Dull, dull, dull.

00:26:52.400 --> 00:26:55.920
Dull, dull, dull.

00:26:56.119 --> 00:26:58.400
Dull, dull.

00:27:01.000 --> 00:27:02.119
Alright, Martin.

00:27:02.759 --> 00:27:03.680
The money is yours.

00:27:03.799 --> 00:27:05.000
I respect your choice.

00:27:06.400 --> 00:27:08.519
When you're back in New York, let's have a couple of drinks.

00:27:17.039 --> 00:27:17.640
Uncle Tong.

00:27:17.640 --> 00:27:19.359
Kid, come to my room quickly.

00:27:19.359 --> 00:27:21.680
Give me some feedback on my script. Come on.

00:27:21.680 --> 00:27:22.359
That...

00:27:23.000 --> 00:27:24.480
Story about some CEO or something?

00:27:24.480 --> 00:27:25.559
Yeah.

00:27:25.559 --> 00:27:28.000
I thought you'd be perfect to ask, I'm stuck here.

00:27:28.000 --> 00:27:29.599
Let's go, come on, hurry up.

00:27:29.599 --> 00:27:30.160
I'm stuck here.

00:27:30.160 --> 00:27:30.839
Is it appropriate?

00:27:30.839 --> 00:27:32.279
Can't really figure this out.

00:27:32.640 --> 00:27:34.839
Actually, the story itself isn't too bad.

00:27:35.480 --> 00:27:36.799
It's just not very realistic.

00:27:37.200 --> 00:27:39.960
Corporate espionage, daily cash burning.

00:27:40.119 --> 00:27:42.319
Being a CEO isn't that easy either.

00:27:43.200 --> 00:27:44.400
But as for Uncle Tong...

00:27:44.720 --> 00:27:46.000
He's been an artsy type for seventy years.

00:27:46.160 --> 00:27:47.359
Optimistic his whole life.

00:27:47.920 --> 00:27:48.880
It's understandable.

00:27:49.319 --> 00:27:50.079
Besides,

00:27:50.240 --> 00:27:51.599
he's so old now.

00:27:51.880 --> 00:27:53.519
Who can possibly change him?

00:27:53.880 --> 00:27:54.720
Actually, there is someone.

00:27:55.519 --> 00:27:56.359
The client.

00:28:02.279 --> 00:28:03.000
Uncle Tong.

00:28:03.079 --> 00:28:04.680
Where's the new episode script you mentioned?

00:28:04.680 --> 00:28:05.559
Is this it?

00:28:07.960 --> 00:28:09.519
Waiting for someone.

00:28:10.160 --> 00:28:10.920
Waiting for who?

00:28:16.920 --> 00:28:17.799
Grandpa Tong

00:28:20.319 --> 00:28:21.759
Speak of the devil

00:28:21.759 --> 00:28:23.039
Quick, have a seat. Sit, sit, sit.

00:28:23.640 --> 00:28:24.759
Sit, sit.

00:28:24.759 --> 00:28:26.359
Here, have some tea. Tea.

00:28:27.000 --> 00:28:27.839
Thank you, Uncle Tong.

00:28:28.240 --> 00:28:29.599
Here's the thing.

00:28:29.880 --> 00:28:31.519
My client...

00:28:32.599 --> 00:28:35.559
wants me to add...

00:28:35.640 --> 00:28:38.079
a more sophisticated romance subplot for the male lead.

00:28:38.720 --> 00:28:40.079
I thought about it, and you two...

00:28:40.079 --> 00:28:41.839
just came back from abroad.

00:28:41.839 --> 00:28:43.599
Both are very sophisticated.

00:28:44.039 --> 00:28:46.079
So, how about it? Help me brainstorm.

00:28:50.759 --> 00:28:52.720
Grandpa Tong, he looks like a real ladies' man.

00:28:53.480 --> 00:28:54.279
He definitely knows...

00:28:54.279 --> 00:28:55.519
how to write that romance plot.

00:28:55.519 --> 00:28:56.359
Yeah.

00:28:56.359 --> 00:28:57.480
I'm sure I can't write it.

00:28:57.480 --> 00:28:59.559
Where are you going? Sit, sit, sit.

00:29:00.119 --> 00:29:01.599
You just got here and you're already leaving?

00:29:02.240 --> 00:29:03.559
Take a look at the script.

00:29:07.680 --> 00:29:08.799
Today...

00:29:09.759 --> 00:29:11.000
I need to record some audio.

00:29:11.000 --> 00:29:12.039
Sorry about this.

00:29:12.039 --> 00:29:13.759
Apologies, apologies.

00:29:17.119 --> 00:29:19.720
Here's my design.

00:29:20.200 --> 00:29:26.920
A middle-aged man worth over a hundred million...

00:29:28.640 --> 00:29:32.920
and an inexperienced female college student.

00:29:34.799 --> 00:29:38.440
The two meet by chance during a trip.

00:29:38.680 --> 00:29:40.559
It's love at first sight.

00:29:41.640 --> 00:29:42.599
What do you think?

00:29:42.799 --> 00:29:45.839
This plot point is sophisticated enough, right?

00:29:45.839 --> 00:29:47.079
I think it's quite sophisticated.

00:29:47.079 --> 00:29:48.279
Just write it like that, Uncle Tong.

00:29:48.279 --> 00:29:51.039
Wait, wait, wait. Here's the problem.

00:29:51.640 --> 00:29:54.799
Writing this romance plot is easy.

00:29:54.799 --> 00:29:56.720
The key is these two people...

00:29:56.720 --> 00:29:59.279
In their own familiar lives...

00:29:59.400 --> 00:30:02.359
their age, status, social circles...

00:30:02.359 --> 00:30:05.000
The gap is just too, too big.

00:30:05.200 --> 00:30:07.000
How do you...

00:30:07.000 --> 00:30:08.440
how do you move this romance forward?

00:30:08.440 --> 00:30:10.000
Help me figure it out.

00:30:11.599 --> 00:30:12.200
Figure it out.

00:30:15.640 --> 00:30:16.599
Middle-aged man.

00:30:16.599 --> 00:30:18.000
A chance encounter on a trip.

00:30:18.279 --> 00:30:20.240
In an idol drama, it's a story.

00:30:20.240 --> 00:30:21.960
But in real life...

00:30:21.960 --> 00:30:23.200
it's an accident.

00:30:23.200 --> 00:30:24.119
Is that so?

00:30:24.599 --> 00:30:28.319
What if the college girl chases the middle-aged man?

00:30:28.319 --> 00:30:30.079
The audience will definitely call her a gold digger.

00:30:30.279 --> 00:30:31.799
What if it's the middle-aged man...

00:30:31.799 --> 00:30:33.400
chasing the college girl?

00:30:33.400 --> 00:30:34.519
Some people would probably love to watch that.

00:30:34.519 --> 00:30:35.839
But not me.

00:30:36.319 --> 00:30:38.759
Well said, well said. Keep going.

00:30:38.839 --> 00:30:39.400
That's it.

00:30:39.400 --> 00:30:40.920
I was just talking casually, Grandpa Tong.

00:30:41.079 --> 00:30:43.319
Say more, I love hearing it.

00:30:44.319 --> 00:30:45.039
Go on.

00:30:47.240 --> 00:30:49.319
I think that girl probably...

00:30:49.759 --> 00:30:51.359
wouldn't like that guy either.

00:30:51.359 --> 00:30:52.640
After all, that middle-aged man...

00:30:52.640 --> 00:30:53.640
is also quite old.

00:30:53.640 --> 00:30:55.359
And their statuses don't match.

00:30:56.160 --> 00:30:58.240
I don't think the story really works, right?

00:30:58.880 --> 00:30:59.640
What do you think?

00:31:06.160 --> 00:31:07.200
I think so.

00:31:34.359 --> 00:31:36.480
What I just said to Grandpa Tong...

00:31:36.720 --> 00:31:38.039
was only about the script.

00:31:38.240 --> 00:31:39.079
It has nothing to do with me personally.

00:31:39.079 --> 00:31:40.440
Because I don't believe in love.

00:31:41.319 --> 00:31:42.039
Same here.

00:31:43.079 --> 00:31:43.720
Good.

00:31:43.799 --> 00:31:45.920
Then let's consider it settled from now on.

00:31:45.920 --> 00:31:48.000
I'll just consider you another uncle.

00:31:49.279 --> 00:31:49.960
Whatever.

00:31:50.759 --> 00:31:51.960
I have another question.

00:31:55.359 --> 00:31:56.599
Since you're not short on money...

00:31:56.599 --> 00:31:58.000
and you don't like the people in the *hutong*...

00:31:58.440 --> 00:31:59.799
why do you insist on squeezing in here?

00:32:01.000 --> 00:32:01.799
Don't worry.

00:32:01.920 --> 00:32:03.079
I won't be staying much longer.

00:32:06.799 --> 00:32:07.480
Right.

00:32:07.559 --> 00:32:09.000
We actually met a long time ago.

00:32:09.119 --> 00:32:10.279
One year ago.

00:32:10.559 --> 00:32:11.599
Back then...

00:32:11.599 --> 00:32:13.960
I never imagined he'd become my Uncle Ma.

00:32:14.799 --> 00:32:16.039
A martini, please.

00:32:21.039 --> 00:32:21.880
Thank you.

00:32:44.640 --> 00:32:45.720
Chinese?

00:32:48.160 --> 00:32:49.000
Chinese.

00:32:50.759 --> 00:32:52.079
You were here yesterday too.

00:32:52.359 --> 00:32:52.960
Yes.

00:32:53.400 --> 00:32:55.119
What a coincidence, running into you again.

00:32:56.960 --> 00:32:58.200
Buy me a drink.

00:32:59.720 --> 00:33:01.359
One whiskey.

00:33:03.759 --> 00:33:05.640
Why are you always alone?

00:33:06.279 --> 00:33:07.000
Am I?

00:33:07.000 --> 00:33:08.480
Yeah. You're new here, right?

00:33:08.640 --> 00:33:10.559
As a longtime local, let me give you some advice.

00:33:10.559 --> 00:33:12.960
This bar isn't the easiest place to make friends.

00:33:14.599 --> 00:33:15.480
Really.

00:33:16.440 --> 00:33:19.279
The cheesy script of a middle-aged man and a college girl.

00:33:19.279 --> 00:33:20.960
I guessed about eighty percent of it right.

00:33:21.200 --> 00:33:23.119
But with our character settings...

00:33:23.119 --> 00:33:25.000
I bet even Grandpa Tong wouldn't dare write it.

00:33:25.000 --> 00:33:25.839
Uncle Wang.

00:33:26.200 --> 00:33:27.839
Tongtong, you're back just in time.

00:33:27.839 --> 00:33:29.400
Say hello to your Uncle Ma.

00:33:29.559 --> 00:33:31.160
My cousin's daughter, Jin Tong.

00:33:31.839 --> 00:33:34.160
She'll be staying long-term at Courtyard 36 from now on.

00:33:34.160 --> 00:33:35.440
She might cause some disturbance.

00:33:35.559 --> 00:33:36.519
Please be understanding.

00:33:41.519 --> 00:33:43.279
Hello. I've heard so much about you.

00:33:43.279 --> 00:33:44.480
Seeing you is better than just hearing about you.

00:33:46.039 --> 00:33:48.440
Baofang Hutong is truly a magical place.

00:33:49.400 --> 00:33:51.720
Letting us reunite with new roles.

00:33:53.519 --> 00:33:56.279
As for why Uncle Ma insists on squeezing in here...

00:33:56.359 --> 00:33:57.880
it's definitely not because of me.

00:33:58.559 --> 00:33:59.759
However...

00:34:00.319 --> 00:34:02.359
I am a bit curious about the reason.

00:34:10.519 --> 00:34:11.519
Jin Tong asked me...

00:34:11.639 --> 00:34:12.800
why I'm squeezing in here.

00:34:13.280 --> 00:34:14.159
I don't know.

00:34:14.480 --> 00:34:15.440
Even less do I know...

00:34:15.440 --> 00:34:16.920
how to explain this thing between her and me...

00:34:16.920 --> 00:34:18.639
to Lianbao and the others.

00:34:19.280 --> 00:34:20.159
Looking at it this way...

00:34:20.400 --> 00:34:21.920
coming back was really a mistake.

00:34:28.119 --> 00:34:29.639
Are you kidding me?

00:34:29.800 --> 00:34:30.920
Seriously, Lianbao.

00:34:31.039 --> 00:34:32.320
We were all there.

00:34:32.760 --> 00:34:33.599
Qiu'er.

00:34:33.880 --> 00:34:36.199
Use your head and think carefully.

00:34:36.199 --> 00:34:38.239
Why would he just give you a house for no reason?

00:34:38.559 --> 00:34:40.679
He said it's so I can take care of Auntie.

00:34:40.679 --> 00:34:43.159
Xiao Fangzi and her husband are taking care of Auntie.

00:34:43.480 --> 00:34:45.280
He should buy them a house too then.

00:34:45.280 --> 00:34:46.440
Right, it doesn't make sense.

00:34:46.440 --> 00:34:47.519
This whole thing is fishy.

00:34:47.519 --> 00:34:49.719
No, Weiguo said he feels...

00:34:50.000 --> 00:34:52.159
...that Tang Zhixin seems a bit untrustworthy.

00:34:52.440 --> 00:34:52.920
That's not it.

00:34:53.159 --> 00:34:54.719
How many times has he even met the guy?

00:34:54.719 --> 00:34:55.639
And he already doesn't trust him?

00:34:55.800 --> 00:34:56.760
Isn't this clearly...

00:34:56.760 --> 00:34:58.400
...the kind of talk online scammers use?

00:34:59.079 --> 00:34:59.840
As for me...

00:34:59.840 --> 00:35:01.320
...I've already sent someone to check him out.

00:35:01.679 --> 00:35:03.519
There's definitely a scheme here.

00:35:03.639 --> 00:35:04.400
I think...

00:35:04.400 --> 00:35:07.159
...he probably has his eye on our Old Wang's Peng Le Xuan.

00:35:09.440 --> 00:35:10.239
Big brother.

00:35:10.880 --> 00:35:13.400
Could he be after Auntie's inheritance?

00:35:13.400 --> 00:35:14.159
That's unlikely.

00:35:14.159 --> 00:35:15.519
He's so rich from America.

00:35:15.519 --> 00:35:16.840
Unlikely, very unlikely.

00:35:17.480 --> 00:35:19.960
Scammers always package themselves well.

00:35:19.960 --> 00:35:21.519
Who knows if his money is real or fake?

00:35:21.519 --> 00:35:22.519
Lianbao is right.

00:35:22.519 --> 00:35:23.239
These rich people...

00:35:23.239 --> 00:35:25.760
...the richer they are, the craftier and more calculating.

00:35:26.000 --> 00:35:28.360
Don't even mention an old neighbor unseen for twenty years.

00:35:28.480 --> 00:35:29.960
Even blood brothers...

00:35:29.960 --> 00:35:32.039
...don't just drop a house on you right away.

00:35:32.239 --> 00:35:34.519
He must have never met truly rich people.

00:35:34.519 --> 00:35:35.760
He's just acting based on his own imagination...

00:35:35.760 --> 00:35:37.199
...playing the part of a generous man.

00:35:37.360 --> 00:35:39.519
Little did he know he'd run into our Lianbao.

00:35:39.519 --> 00:35:41.039
Lianbao is a truly rich man.

00:35:41.039 --> 00:35:42.960
He saw right through his flaws.

00:35:43.559 --> 00:35:45.280
Me, I wouldn't call myself rich.

00:35:45.280 --> 00:35:46.199
You're being modest.

00:35:46.199 --> 00:35:47.000
But...

00:35:47.000 --> 00:35:48.880
...I deal with rich people a lot.

00:35:48.880 --> 00:35:50.199
He is definitely not...

00:35:56.760 --> 00:35:58.039
The letter's here!

00:35:58.039 --> 00:35:59.679
I'll open it, you see for yourselves.

00:36:00.679 --> 00:36:01.480
Look.

00:36:02.159 --> 00:36:03.880
Big brother, you look too.

00:36:07.239 --> 00:36:08.960
You'd better take a look yourself first.

00:36:10.280 --> 00:36:12.199
I told you Weiguo definitely wouldn't lie to me.

00:36:12.599 --> 00:36:13.719
I'm off to work.

00:36:14.880 --> 00:36:15.719
Qiu'er!

00:36:15.840 --> 00:36:19.280
Qiu'er really hit the jackpot this time.

00:36:21.840 --> 00:36:22.559
Big brother.

00:36:22.679 --> 00:36:24.480
I think we should go with him.

00:36:25.079 --> 00:36:25.840
Go where?

00:36:26.039 --> 00:36:28.400
We can't let Ma Weiguo lead Qiu'er astray again.

00:36:30.079 --> 00:36:31.000
Big brother.

00:36:39.559 --> 00:36:40.159
Morning.

00:36:46.840 --> 00:36:47.639
Weiguo.

00:36:49.480 --> 00:36:51.079
Big brother and second brother said...

00:36:51.079 --> 00:36:52.079
...to come along and take a look.

00:36:52.079 --> 00:36:53.119
Help give some advice.

00:36:54.000 --> 00:36:55.519
Qiu'er is too honest.

00:36:55.719 --> 00:36:57.000
We're afraid he'll get tricked.

00:36:57.599 --> 00:36:59.320
Going with him, no objections, right?

00:36:59.320 --> 00:37:00.079
No objections.

00:37:00.079 --> 00:37:02.079
Let's go. That Xiao Hu is waiting there.

00:37:02.079 --> 00:37:04.559
No need. I have plenty of connections here.

00:37:04.639 --> 00:37:05.760
All good properties.

00:37:27.920 --> 00:37:28.760
This is the place?

00:37:28.760 --> 00:37:29.719
Yes, yes, right here.

00:37:30.280 --> 00:37:32.239
This... this place doesn't look cheap.

00:37:32.679 --> 00:37:34.719
This is peanuts for Boss Ma.

00:37:34.719 --> 00:37:35.639
Right, Boss Ma?

00:37:35.840 --> 00:37:37.599
Then let Qiu'er see if she likes it first.

00:37:37.920 --> 00:37:39.360
What a show-off.

00:37:40.880 --> 00:37:42.039
Where are you going?

00:37:43.320 --> 00:37:44.880
What are you two doing?

00:37:45.639 --> 00:37:47.079
Isn't he trying to buy you off?

00:37:47.320 --> 00:37:49.360
Then I'll test just how capable he really is.

00:37:49.920 --> 00:37:51.400
If he's all talk and no action,

00:37:51.400 --> 00:37:52.039
I'll make him

00:37:52.039 --> 00:37:53.559
too ashamed to stay in Baofang Hutong.

00:37:53.679 --> 00:37:54.559
Can you two

00:37:54.559 --> 00:37:56.360
not involve innocent bystanders?

00:37:56.360 --> 00:37:57.199
Listen up.

00:37:57.199 --> 00:37:59.000
Keep your knees locked straight.

00:37:59.320 --> 00:38:00.400
Don't just kneel the moment someone

00:38:00.400 --> 00:38:01.239
promises to buy you a house.

00:38:01.239 --> 00:38:02.400
That's pathetic.

00:38:02.400 --> 00:38:04.480
Kneel for one house? Don't be ridiculous.

00:38:04.480 --> 00:38:05.960
I'd kneel for a jianbing pancake.

00:38:05.960 --> 00:38:07.360
Stop joking around with me, will you?

00:38:08.679 --> 00:38:09.880
Look at you two.

00:38:10.079 --> 00:38:12.000
You, with the family restaurant, are the "win-by-doing-nothing" type.

00:38:12.000 --> 00:38:13.679
What's the "win-by-doing-nothing" type?

00:38:14.039 --> 00:38:15.559
And you, a company executive,

00:38:15.559 --> 00:38:17.719
are the "996 blessing" type.

00:38:21.119 --> 00:38:22.199
Can you possibly understand

00:38:22.199 --> 00:38:24.440
the helplessness and bitterness of living paycheck to paycheck?

00:38:26.960 --> 00:38:27.960
Manager Li, look.

00:38:27.960 --> 00:38:29.079
This house of ours

00:38:29.079 --> 00:38:31.639
was designed by a famous Nordic designer.

00:38:31.880 --> 00:38:33.719
You see, the overall style

00:38:33.719 --> 00:38:34.599
is modern.

00:38:34.599 --> 00:38:36.440
It incorporates minimalist elements.

00:38:36.880 --> 00:38:38.679
You can look at our furniture;

00:38:38.679 --> 00:38:40.760
it's all internationally renowned brands.

00:38:40.880 --> 00:38:42.440
Five... five burners!

00:38:42.440 --> 00:38:44.199
I could cook dumplings in five pots!

00:38:44.199 --> 00:38:46.119
One dumpling per pot, no flavor mixing!

00:38:46.559 --> 00:38:47.239
This is fun.

00:38:47.239 --> 00:38:49.239
Manager Li, please, this way, this way.

00:38:49.760 --> 00:38:51.239
Our master bedroom here

00:38:51.360 --> 00:38:53.000
has excellent natural light.

00:38:53.559 --> 00:38:56.119
Imagine waking up, having a coffee,

00:38:56.119 --> 00:38:57.519
then opening the window for a gentle breeze.

00:38:57.519 --> 00:38:58.360
Careful!

00:38:58.360 --> 00:38:59.840
How pleasant, right?

00:39:01.719 --> 00:39:03.599
Don't act like you've never seen anything nice.

00:39:03.599 --> 00:39:06.440
Truly north-south through ventilation, excellent light.

00:39:06.440 --> 00:39:07.280
This property of ours

00:39:07.280 --> 00:39:09.320
is highly sought-after in the capital.

00:39:09.320 --> 00:39:12.119
It's perfect for high-income individuals like you.

00:39:12.760 --> 00:39:13.719
I'm not the one buying it.

00:39:14.639 --> 00:39:15.599
It's perfect for...

00:39:15.599 --> 00:39:16.559
I'm not buying it either.

00:39:20.039 --> 00:39:21.800
It's perfect for your kind of...

00:39:21.800 --> 00:39:23.960
Miss, he's buying it for her.

00:39:25.920 --> 00:39:27.039
What do you mean?

00:39:27.039 --> 00:39:28.199
I'm standing right here in the middle,

00:39:28.199 --> 00:39:29.320
and you just skip over me?

00:39:29.320 --> 00:39:30.480
Stop fooling around.

00:39:30.480 --> 00:39:31.480
Let me ask you.

00:39:32.079 --> 00:39:35.400
Are you satisfied with this house?

00:39:38.079 --> 00:39:39.119
It's pretty good.

00:39:40.480 --> 00:39:42.119
Let me ask you again.

00:39:42.440 --> 00:39:43.960
Are you satisfied?

00:39:47.519 --> 00:39:48.280
It's okay.

00:39:48.840 --> 00:39:50.360
Did you hear that, Boss Ma?

00:39:50.599 --> 00:39:51.920
Qiu'er is very satisfied.

00:39:51.920 --> 00:39:53.320
It's just a little pricey.

00:39:53.519 --> 00:39:54.840
That's not a problem for you, right?

00:39:54.840 --> 00:39:55.599
Not expensive.

00:39:55.960 --> 00:39:56.880
This is much cheaper

00:39:56.880 --> 00:39:58.559
than the courtyard house I showed Qiu'er yesterday.

00:39:58.559 --> 00:39:59.480
A lot cheaper.

00:40:00.719 --> 00:40:01.440
Qiu'er,

00:40:01.440 --> 00:40:03.519
since you like it, let's pay.

00:40:03.960 --> 00:40:04.639
Wait.

00:40:06.400 --> 00:40:08.719
You said this is two bedrooms, one living room, right?

00:40:10.119 --> 00:40:11.440
I think it's a bit small.

00:40:11.440 --> 00:40:12.320
Right, big brother?

00:40:14.480 --> 00:40:15.559
This is too small.

00:40:15.559 --> 00:40:17.519
Do you have anything bigger? This won't do.

00:40:17.679 --> 00:40:18.719
Actually, I think this house...

00:40:18.719 --> 00:40:19.480
Don't think about it.

00:40:19.480 --> 00:40:20.639
Let's go, let's go, look at something else.

00:40:22.639 --> 00:40:23.559
Sir, take another look.

00:40:23.559 --> 00:40:25.320
We also have three-bedroom, one-living-room units.

00:40:25.320 --> 00:40:27.320
Come, this way please, watch your step.

00:40:27.320 --> 00:40:27.840
Alright.

00:40:27.960 --> 00:40:28.800
Our surrounding

00:40:28.800 --> 00:40:30.719
living facilities and commercial amenities

00:40:30.719 --> 00:40:31.840
are extremely comprehensive.

00:40:31.840 --> 00:40:33.039
And it includes

00:40:33.039 --> 00:40:35.320
top schools from kindergarten through high school.

00:40:35.320 --> 00:40:36.679
When you have children in the future,

00:40:36.679 --> 00:40:37.440
getting them to and from school

00:40:37.440 --> 00:40:38.840
will be very convenient.

00:40:38.840 --> 00:40:39.840
To own a townhouse

00:40:39.840 --> 00:40:41.159
in a location like this

00:40:41.159 --> 00:40:43.199
is truly a rare opportunity.

00:40:43.199 --> 00:40:44.199
Come, this way please.

00:40:44.199 --> 00:40:45.920
Do I even have the fate to live in a villa?

00:40:45.920 --> 00:40:46.800
Let me tell you something.

00:40:46.800 --> 00:40:48.000
Don't be so spineless.

00:40:48.000 --> 00:40:49.159
Keep your knees locked straight.

00:40:49.159 --> 00:40:50.000
Don't you dare kneel.

00:40:50.679 --> 00:40:51.440
Boss Ma,

00:40:51.440 --> 00:40:52.400
don't think it's too expensive.

00:40:52.519 --> 00:40:54.000
This is all for Qiu'er's sake.

00:40:54.760 --> 00:40:55.400
Qiu'er,

00:40:55.400 --> 00:40:56.559
just see if you like it.

00:40:56.559 --> 00:40:58.039
If you like it, we'll sign the contract.

00:40:58.559 --> 00:40:59.679
Really?

00:40:59.679 --> 00:41:00.559
Then let's sit inside.

00:41:00.559 --> 00:41:01.679
I'll go prepare the documents now.

00:41:01.679 --> 00:41:02.320
No, no, no.

00:41:02.320 --> 00:41:03.199
Hold on, hold on, hold on.

00:41:04.000 --> 00:41:04.800
Looking at it this way,

00:41:04.800 --> 00:41:07.320
I still feel it's lacking something.

00:41:07.320 --> 00:41:08.039
How do I remember

00:41:08.039 --> 00:41:10.440
Uncle Tong likes living in that hutong?

00:41:10.440 --> 00:41:11.320
Right, big brother?

00:41:12.440 --> 00:41:13.440
What?

00:41:13.719 --> 00:41:14.519
It's a villa!

00:41:14.519 --> 00:41:15.679
My dad's opinion isn't important.

00:41:15.679 --> 00:41:16.800
Who says it's not important?

00:41:17.320 --> 00:41:19.320
Filial piety, filial piety. What does it mean?

00:41:19.320 --> 00:41:20.679
Filial piety means

00:41:20.679 --> 00:41:23.039
you have to follow the elder's wishes, right?

00:41:23.039 --> 00:41:23.960
Never heard of that.

00:41:23.960 --> 00:41:25.199
Let's go, let's go, let's look at something else.

00:41:25.199 --> 00:41:26.360
What? What?

00:41:26.360 --> 00:41:27.760
What do you mean look at something else?

00:41:27.760 --> 00:41:29.480
I... the mood was built up to this point, big brother!

00:41:29.480 --> 00:41:30.480
This won't do, won't do.

00:41:30.480 --> 00:41:31.320
This still isn't good enough?

00:41:31.320 --> 00:41:31.840
It's fine.

00:41:31.840 --> 00:41:32.320
I'll take you to see more.

00:41:32.320 --> 00:41:32.800
Don't mind them.

00:41:32.800 --> 00:41:33.280
Where to?

00:41:33.280 --> 00:41:33.800
Sorry about that.

00:41:33.800 --> 00:41:34.559
Come with me.

00:41:34.559 --> 00:41:35.199
Where to?

00:41:35.199 --> 00:41:36.079
Go where?